embassy Saturday, saying he was deeply shocked by the "inhuman"
incident that happened in a peaceful country like Tanzania.
</P>
<P>
Juma said the government will give full support to the
investigation into the incident which was caused by a blast of an
oil tanker outside the embassy on Friday morning.
</P>
